Very good. We served at a dinner party by 'stuffing' the endive leaves and then drizzling the sauce on top before passing around. The sauce could use more flavour - maybe more cayenne? - and the green pepper was overwhelming. I would recommend reducing or eliminating the green pepper altogether.

